then I'd stay with them and do my research at Oxford,

59
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:42,570
如果给我一等学位  我就能去剑桥了
but if they gave me the 1st, I needed to get into Cambridge, then

60
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:45,070
