- They gave you the 1st. - They gave me the 1st.

62
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:53,460
-是啊  -派对已经正式结束了
- Of course. - This party is officially deceased.

63
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,970
来吧  我找辆车送你回家
Come on, I've fixed you up a ride home.

64
