- Well, it was lovely to talk to you. - Yes.

66
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:09,870
还有  希望你能找到那个方程
And... I hope you find your equation.

67
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,530
是啊
Yes... oh...

68
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:16,820
-再见  -再见
- Bye. - G'bye.

69
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,700
斯蒂芬
Stephen?

70
