来看看这个
Well, then, here we are,

72
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:43,310
给你们的小测试
a little challenge for you all,

73
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:45,760
在你们的学术研究路上...
as you embark upon your separate doctoral journeys...

74
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:47,870
