75
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:49,940
传下去
Pass them down.

76
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,170
来看看你们是男人还是男孩
Something to separate the men from the boys,

77
00:05:52,170 --> 00:05:53,380
是粮食还是糟糠
the wheat from the chaff,

